data.description:
Great starter Townhouse in one of the most well located quadrants of the city. Do you need to have access to I20 or I70, then this is your ticket. The house is well kept and ready for you to add your personal touches.
The house comes with a built in Water Softener and has beautiful grown trees. 
Come find out for yourself.
